reviewText: Two of these "8 Movies" are great (for the $$ 2 out of 8 is not bad I guess)"Babe" sequel and "2 Brothers" are swell. The direct to DVD "Beethoven" movies aren't even movies and the rest is crap, but on the cheap, crap can be and usually is fun. But that monkey baseball movie is soooo stupid.
Wonderful family-friendly movies at a great price with several movies.
Great old shows I bought to share with my 6 year old son which he enjoys watching them
Good run time, some of my favorite children's movies, all on one dvd....so is handy....purchased for my five year old niece, she liked it.
My 8 year old niece loves these movies! Great bang for you buck
Gave to the grandkids for Christmas they seemed to enjoy it very much
great  for long car rides since there are 8 movies on 1 disc.  my daughter is all about the animals
What a great collection of movies. Got for a gift
We watched these for Thanksgiving with the kids ....all 8 movies was great!
We have not watched all of the movies yet but the ones we have watched are good for the family.
Great set of fun kids movies. My 3 year old loves to watch them one after another.
cute movies for the whole family!
My grandson has just discovered movies, and he is allowed to watch them for short periods of time.  These are a few of the favorites his mother watched when she was little.
all those movies are very cute some  of the movies are very funny I like it
Arrived on time. Great price for 8 movies.
very entertaining for my great grandson

If this information is given, I sure can't find it! I might be able to tell what movies are on this DVD if I use a magnifying glass! Why isn't this info listed in the description? I'll pass on this one.
Great collection and a very nice bargain!  Kids got a lot of use out of this during a recent road trip.
A lot of great movies for one low price!
Seriously, for five buck you can't go wrong with this. My young daughters really like these classic movies. Safe G/PG rated movies.
My kids love this collection. They are 5 and 7 yrs old. Very good price for 8 movies.
Great movies for a rainy day
My daughter loves all of these movies
A great combination of family friendly movies
Bought for a friend; I'm sure they're enjoying it.

Great for children (and adults) that love the older animal movies, not that animated stuff! Just purchased this for my soon to be 3 year old son and he loves it! Provides him the ability to "pick a movie" without dragging out all his movies from the shelf! Very good deal even for the price... I paid $7 for this set, which is less than $1 a movie! That's cheaper than renting a movie for a night at Redbox.. Plus for the ones he really enjoys he can even own and keep. This set will definatly pay for itself in just a couple of days (:
This is a present for my grandson.
Great animal based family movies.  My 7 and 9 year loved them.  Great deal!!!
We love this movie pack, what an amazing deal on several great family movies!!

So far we have only watched Babe - Pig in the City (every night for the last 3 days) but that movie alone is more than worth the cost of this 8 pack of movies.  The quality is good, the movie is adorable and the value is excellent at $5.00
Love all of these movies. Fun to watch.
great for entertaining the kids on rainy or cold days
Excellent gift package for a child. You'll want to check and see how many of these they already have, but this is a great starter package for one who doesn't have a big collection.
My daughter is obsessed with this DVD collection, as it kept her busy the entire 12 hours to the beach. Would highly recommend!!
